Generate in 4K HD, 16:9 aspect ratio, with ultra‑realistic, 8K‑grade texture fidelity.

The style is an uncompromising masterwork of Neo‑Ukiyo‑e woodblock technique, Zen Sumi‑e ink‑wash, and mariner’s cartography, kissed by the southern sun and blessed by the spirit of freedom.

